{
  "stem": "8423.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we would have preferred to go in the evening, you know, when we weren't so visible.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, there was no such a thing, because there was the curfew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't let us out past a certain hour, so we certainly couldn't go in the dark.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then if some of the children had to go during the night, you know, and they would go someplace outside the barrack, because you couldn't go any place else, then we had hell to catch the next day.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were called pigs and all this sort of stuff, you know-- dirty swine and all that, because the children had to go to the bathroom.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was life in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And again, the young people had gotten together, and they were helping, you know, out the older people, doing whatever they could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they even had, like, a storehouse from the stuff that they bought in there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they tried to do, you know, as much as they could.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they had a makeshift hospital set up there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And some of the young boys had formed a little underground group, where they had smuggled in some ammunition.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were going to blow up the trains, when they came to take us to Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they never got to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because first of all, they were told that if there was any kind of retaliation or any kind of-- whatever it's called, they are going to kill all the people in the infirmity first.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, resistance, that's the word I was looking for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Any resistance, that they would kill all the people in the infirmity first.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there would be just no reason to do it, because they have so many means in getting us there.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
